        {
            "id": 6439957,
            "title": "中東風險降溫帶動買氣，道瓊開盤上揚蘋果勁揚5%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><img alt=\"Reuters/TPG\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6439957/o/3bad8bef9e07ecb8f2b48ff872388939.jpg\"/></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>2026年05月01日（優分析／產業數據中心報導）⸺ 美股1日開盤上揚，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊工業指數</a>上漲192.48點。市場對中東局勢的避險情緒降溫，加上企業財報優於預期，帶動買盤回流。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section><p>伊朗官方媒體報導，伊朗已透過巴基斯坦向美國提出新的停火談判方案，市場解讀為伊朗釋出協商意願。受此影響，WTI 6月原油期貨跌至每桶約$101，較前一日收盤下跌逾3%，進一步支撐投資信心。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>個股方面，蘋果Apple(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AAPL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AAPL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AAPL-US</a>)股價一度上漲4.5%。該公司2026年第一季營收與淨利均優於市場預期，第二季（4至6月）營收展望也優於市場預期，毛利率表現穩健。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>同樣公布財報的默克Merck(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MRK:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MRK\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MRK-US</a>)獲買盤青睞。前一日承壓的科技股也見反彈，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊</a>成分股中，微軟Microsoft(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MSFT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MSFT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MSFT-US</a>)、輝達NVIDIA(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NVDA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NVDA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NVDA-US</a>)、Salesforce(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRM-US</a>)同步走高。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>不過，指數漲勢仍受限制。由於標普500指數與<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">那斯達克綜合指數</a>前一日雙雙改寫歷史新高，週末前部分大型股出現獲利了結賣壓。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>其他<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊</a>成分股中，開拓重工Caterpillar(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CAT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CAT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CAT-US</a>)、思科Cisco(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CSCO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CSCO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CSCO-US</a>)、Visa(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:V:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/V\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">V-US</a>)上漲；家得寶Home Depot(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:HD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/HD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">HD-US</a>)、嬌生公司J&amp;J(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:JNJ:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/JNJ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">JNJ-US</a>)下跌，公布財報的安進Amgen(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMGN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMGN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMGN-US</a>)也遭賣壓。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">那斯達克綜合指數</a>則連續第三個交易日開高，Palantir Technologies(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:PLTR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/PLTR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">PLTR-US</a>)、特斯拉Tesla(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSLA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSLA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSLA-US</a>)、英特爾Intel(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTC-US</a>)等科技股表現強勢。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>※ 本文經「優分析」授權轉載，原文出處:<a href=\"https://uanalyze.com.tw/articles/7132851345\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"color:#A9A9A9\">原文連結</a>\n<br/>※ 免責聲明：文中所提的個股、基金、期貨商品內容僅供參考，並非投資建議，投資人應獨立判斷，審慎評估風險。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p></p></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6439957",
